Package: nlbayes
Type: Package
Title: Noisy Logic Bayesian Inference
Version: 0.2.1
Date: 2025-01-22
Author: Argenis Arriojas
Maintainer: Argenis Arriojas <ArriojasMaldonado001@umb.edu>
Description: An implementation of an MCMC algorithm for inference in noisy Logic
    graphical models. The package uses Bayesian networks to infer active
    transcription factors from gene expression data.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/umbibio/nlbayes-r
BugReports: https://github.com/umbibio/nlbayes-r/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    methods,
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.8),
    RcppProgress (>= 0.1),
    rjson,
    pROC,
    dplyr,
    txtplot
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp,
    RcppProgress
Suggests:
    devtools,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
SystemRequirements: GNU GSL
